# M — U+004D. ONE continuous stroked path (left stem -> top flat -> diagonal to the V
# apex -> diagonal up -> right top flat -> right stem) so the middle V is a clean join
# with NO notch at the bottom. Uniform stroke 84. Apex at (444,40) so the V foot grounds
# on the baseline.
advance 888
stroke 84
M 136 0
L 136 658
L 220 658
L 444 40
L 669 658
L 750 658
L 750 0
